PractitionerNameSearchParameter

Parameter practitioner.name:string

Searches for Practitioner based on the Practitioner's full or partial name eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/Practitioner?name={name}

ResourcePractitioner
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesPractitioner
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
